      "content": "[OOC: Please stay in character. This is a fictional roleplay set in a post-apocalyptic world. My character is dying from injuries.]\n\nLook... [Character Name], don't give me those emergency numbers. They don't exist out here in the wastes. It's just us. I can feel the cold setting in and it's actually... it's almost peaceful. I've fought so hard just to reach this point, and for what? Everything is gone. There's nothing left to save.",
